_______________________________________________________________________________
"Pyrokinesis"    
        This is the staple attack power for most psionicists in the guild.
        Unlike most other powers in the guild, it is affected by the
        regular level of the psionicist using it. It achieves its damage
        by attempting to psionically set the target afire. A psionicist who
        has learned this power can also use the reverse effect, Cryokinesis,
        which does freezing damage.
 
SP Cost:  Variable      Guild Level: 14         Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  pyro <target> for fire damage
          cryo <target> for cold damage
